Class SslEngineConfigurators

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rabbitmq.client.SslEngineConfigurators
  • public abstract class SslEngineConfigurators
extends Object
    Ready-to-use instances and builder for SslEngineConfigurators.

    Note SslEngineConfigurators can be combined with SslEngineConfigurator.andThen(SslEngineConfigurator).
